import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
import Singin from '../components/SignIn/Signin'
import MainLayout from '../container/MainLayout'
import AdDevices from '../components/Devices/AdDevices'
import UsDevices from '../components/Devices/UsDevices'
import MaDevices from '../components/Devices/MaDevices'
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
export default function MainRouter() {
    return (
        <Router>
            <Switch>
                <Route exact path='/' component={Singin} />
                <Route path='/db'>
                    <MainLayout>
                        <Switch>
                            <Route path='/db/devives' component={AdDevices} />
                            <Route path='/db/manage-devices' component={MaDevices} />


                            <Route path='/db/u-devives' component={UsDevices} />

                        </Switch>
                    </MainLayout>
                </Route>

            </Switch>
        </Router>
    )
}
